# Codelabs

These are sessions for developers to familiarise yourself with the new GOV.UK kubernetes cluster.

- App configuration and deployment using the govuk helm chart

- App update, deployment, monitoring and logs using a test app

## Before starting

Please update the #govuk-replatforming-codelab channel by adding your slack id to the seat you will be using during your codelab session.

## After your codelab session

Please update the #govuk-replatforming-codelab channel by setting `free` to the seat you have used during your codelab session.
